data.description: Wonderful Updates: HOA recently updated the decking on the balcony off the primary bedroom and the deck off the back of the condo to Composite. They have also repaved the parking area. Come check out the mountain views from the Primary bedroom balcony! Perfect for that morning cup of coffee or beautiful evening sunset over Cheyenne Mountain. Just 1/2 block to hiking & bike trails at Bear Creek Park, Dog park, and close proximity to downtown, Old Colorado City & Broadmoor Resort. The main level welcomes you to an open floor plan with wood burning fireplace, hardwood floors, kitchen and dining area. There is also a half bath on this level and access to the back deck and storage shed. The kitchen was remodeled with tile flooring and tile countertops. Upstairs is a full bathroom with tile flooring and linen closet. The Primary bedroom has vaulted ceilings and French doors that open to your private balcony facing the mountains. The 2nd bedroom down the hall is good sized with ample closet space. The bonus area is the large basement with washer and dryer. Perfect for adding another bedroom, workout room or storage. This lovely end unit, 2 bed, 1.5 bath townhome is freshly painted on the interior. It also has a newer water heater and Seller to provide a two-year home warranty. Come and enjoy the back deck, balcony off the primary bedroom and front porch!
